> would it be possible to selectively enable all tests via cron?

@edsantiago yes, `$CIRRUS_CRON` will be non-empty if the branch build (job) was triggered by cron.  If you'd like to figure out the `skip:` logic to make that work, please (please!) take that liberty.  I would undoubtedly make it way more complicated than necessary :grin: 

Note:  Contrary to the docs, `$CRON_BRANCH`will be non-empty for both a PR-push AND branch-push.  For a PR it will be set to `pull/<number>` :frowning_face:
